      jsonb_build_object('label', 'A', 'text', '$mvr$', 'image_url', null),
      jsonb_build_object('label', 'B', 'text', '$\frac{1}{2}mv^2$', 'image_url', null),
      jsonb_build_object('label', 'C', 'text', '$0$', 'image_url', null),
      jsonb_build_object('label', 'D', 'text', '$2\pi \frac{mv^2}{r}$', 'image_url', null)
    ),
    '"C"', 4, 1, 'hard',
    'The centripetal force is always perpendicular to the displacement: $$\vec{F_c} \perp d\vec{s}$$ Therefore: $$\vec{F_c} \cdot d\vec{s} = |\vec{F_c}| |d\vec{s}| \cos(90°) = 0$$ Work done: $$W = \int \vec{F_c} \cdot d\vec{s} = 0$$ The centripetal force only changes direction, not speed.',
